# Debug Extension Loading

## Goal
Debug why @agpenton/pi-claude-subagents doesn't appear in the extension list.

## Current State
```
Extension Files:
   ✓ agpenton-pi-claude-subagents/dist/index.js (entry point)
   ✓ agent/extensions/pi-claude-subagents.js (symlink)

Package Registry:
   ✓ npm:@agpenton/pi-claude-subagents added to packages list

Extension Pattern:
   ✓ ~/.pi/agent/extensions/*.ts AND *.js
```

## Steps to Debug

1. Check if Pi.dev can load the extension
2. Look for import errors
3. Try loading extension in Pi.dev context
4. Check extension API structure
5. Verify extension exports work correctly

## Expected Structure
```javascript
export default function(api) {
   // Extension initialization
   return extensionExports;
}
```

## Actual Issues
- Extension needs @earendil-works/pi-coding-agent runtime
- Not available when loading outside Pi.dev context
